### Tag Tests ###

# 1. Create new tag (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/blog/tags/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token_here

{
    "name": "technology"
}

# 2. Get all tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/tags/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

# 3. Get single tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/tags/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Testing Flow ###
# 1. First run the register request
# 2. Then login and copy the access token
# 3. Replace 'your_access_token_here' in the Authorization headers
# 4. Test other endpoints with the token
